  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automatic .m3u8 stream detection via headless Chromium browser (Playwright)",
    "Local HLS proxy that spoofs Chrome TLS fingerprint (curl_cffi) and injects Referer headers",
    "Custom sideloaded Roku channel (BrightScript) controlled via the Roku ECP API",
    "SSDP-based automatic device discovery for Roku and Fire TV on the local network",
    "One-click firewall rule creation for the proxy (UAC-prompted, Windows Firewall)",
    "PC playback test mode via VLC before casting to TV",
    "Clipboard auto-paste for detected URLs",
    "Rotating log file for windowless debugging"
  ],
